description.plain:
A92 is a Drill collective consisting of several drill rappers from Drogheda, Ireland.

They have beef with AV9 of Balbriggan, Ireland.



Known members:


Offica
KSav
Dbo
BT
Kebz
Trapboy
Ace
Nikz
